overview: Join Tut and his friends from the band: Trombone, Jasper Clown, bass, sax and trumpet in their magic and adventure tours by Songs City! This musical trip introduces children to the fun and funny characters and songs. Meet these colorful and musical series inspired by the famous nursery rhyme Wheels
